01:36:27,323 --> 01:36:28,365
- Don't you do that, honey!

01:36:28,407 --> 01:36:29,408
(hollering)

01:36:29,450 --> 01:36:30,284
Yes, yes!

01:36:31,827 --> 01:36:33,662
Oh, man.
