01:50:42,761 --> 01:50:44,304
- So what have you
brought us this time?

01:50:44,346 --> 01:50:46,681
Was your trip
pleasantly uneventful?

01:50:46,723 --> 01:50:48,808
- No, somebody was
following me again.

01:50:48,850 --> 01:50:49,934
I had to shake them.

01:50:49,976 --> 01:50:51,353
Took the subway.

01:50:51,394 --> 01:50:54,856
- Give us your
camera case, please.

01:50:54,898 --> 01:50:57,359
- You must forgive our plan.

01:50:58,568 --> 01:51:01,029
The photographs at your last
drop were not very good,

01:51:01,071 --> 01:51:02,906
every one out of focus.

